        "description": {
          "chat": "",
          "unidentified": "",
          "value": "<p>Each scrap-bot has a base frame determined by its original function, as follows.</p>\n<p><strong>Assembly</strong>: An assembly scrap-bot has an integrated engineering tool kit. It also has Engineering +9.</p>\n<p><strong>Companion</strong>: A companion scrapbot has Diplomacy +4 and Sense Motive +9.</p>\n<p><strong>Delivery</strong>: A delivery scrap-bot is Small and has an extraordinary fly speed of 30 feet with average maneuverability. It also has a storage area that can hold up to 3 bulk.</p>\n<p><strong>Domestic</strong>: A domestic scrap-bot has integrated cleaning systems that allow it to clean items in a 1-foot cube each round. It can reverse cleaning functions to soil a similar area in the same time.</p>\n<p><strong>Security</strong>: A security scrap-bot has a pulsecaster pistol and the integrated weapons universal creature rule. It can make ranged attacks with a +7 attack bonus. The security scrap-bot also has Intimidate +4.</p>"
        },
